description: The Irish chieftain was buried in the same Spanish chapel as Christopher Columbus.
title: Red Hugh: Spanish dig for the bones of 'Fighting Prince of Donegal'
title_page: Red Hugh: Spanish dig for the bones of 'Fighting Prince of Donegal' - BBC News
maintext: The team does not yet know which, if any, of the skeletons recovered so far is that of Red Hugh, but at least two can be ruled out because they were women.
